  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is very important to evaluate the degree of gastrointestinal dysfunction in critical ill
      patients. Thus the investigators conducted transabdominal intestine ultrasonography(US) in
      critical ill patients to evaluated the degree of gastrointestinal dysfunction under the acute
      gastrointestinal injury (AGI)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
